## 可用 Skill 索引

| Skill | 关键参数 | 返回值摘要 |
|-------|----------|------------|
| `create_object` | `name`, `primitive_type`, `x/y/z`, `scale_x/y/z`, `color_r/g/b` | `{success, name}` |
| `find_objects` | `name?`, `tag?`, `component_type?`, `include_inactive=False`, `limit=100` | `{success, count, objects[{name, instanceId, position, components}]}` |
| `move_object` | `instance_id` 或 `name`; `x/y/z?`, `rot_x/y/z?`, `scale_x/y/z?` | `{success, name, position, rotation, scale}` |

完整参数说明（类型、默认值、返回结构）→ `docs/create_object.md`、`docs/find_objects.md`、`docs/move_object.md`

